---
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const pageTitle = 'Best Wireless Charging Station for Desk 2026';
const pageDescription = 'Honest review of 3-in-1 wireless charging stands. Charge phone, watch, and earbuds simultaneously without cable clutter.';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription} />
    <style>
      main { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1rem; line-height: 1.7; color: #333; }
      h1 { color: #232f3e; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
      .meta { color: #666; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 2rem; }
      .product-box { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 1.5rem; margin: 2rem 0; }
      .product-box h2 { margin-top: 0; }
      .product-box ul { padding-left: 1.2rem; }
      .btn { display: inline-block; background: #ff9900; color: #000; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 0.5rem; }
      .btn:hover { background: #e68a00; }
      .disclaimer { font-size: 0.8rem; color: #888; margin-top: 3rem; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 1rem; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>Best Wireless Charging Station for Desk</h1>
      <div class="meta">Updated May 2026 · Under $35</div>

      <p>A desk covered in charging cables looks messy and wastes space. A single 3-in-1 wireless stand replaces three chargers and keeps your phone, watch, and earbuds topped up while you work. After testing multiple options, one stand wins for stability and charging speed.</p>

      <div class="product-box">
        <h2>🏆 3-in-1 Wireless Charging Stand</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>15W phone charging</strong> — fast wireless for iPhone and Android</li>
          <li><strong>5W watch charging</strong> — Apple Watch and Galaxy Watch compatible</li>
          <li><strong>5W earbuds charging</strong> — AirPods Pro and Galaxy Buds ready</li>
          <li><strong>Magnetic alignment</strong> — phone snaps into perfect charging position</li>
          <li><strong>LED indicator</strong> — soft blue light shows charging status, auto-dims at night</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/s?k=3+in+1+wireless+charging+station&tag=toolwise20-20" class="btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored">Check Current Price on Amazon</a>
      </div>

      <h3>Why a stand beats a charging pad</h3>
      <p>Flat charging pads hide under papers and make it hard to see notifications. A vertical stand keeps your phone screen visible for calls and messages while it charges. The 3-in-1 design also means you need only one wall plug — critical when your desk already has a monitor, laptop, and lamp competing for outlets.</p>

      <h3>Who should buy it</h3>
      <p>Anyone with a smartphone, smartwatch, and wireless earbuds who wants a clean desk. It pairs perfectly with our recommended USB-C hub and monitor riser — tuck the charging stand behind the riser and your desk surface stays completely clear of cables.</p>

      <div class="disclaimer">
        Disclosure: As an Amazon Associate I earn from qualifying purchases. This review is based on independent research and reader feedback.
      </div>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>